{"tid":356902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇林子健返屋企沖涼換衫，都唔拆左啲釘先？","createTime":"2017-08-12T12:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T23:48:30.000Z","uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de5b1440a72b40098a29aa985ef62c258f964611","tid":356902,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"據李柱銘所講，林生係西貢醒返之後<br />\n係返咗屋企先，仲要沖涼同洗咗當時身穿嘅衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34acb801b3fee1d5f0fd0dcd62bfd78f23b0cbdd","tid":356902,"uid":79974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"試下俾人捉咪知"},{"pid":"ef8a078ad2d9a585f0b9638b1ed36bded460a4d7","tid":356902,"uid":48631,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:57:16.000Z","msg":"呢單野真係唔好跟車太貼,好易炒車"},{"pid":"ce356aeb0e1d2335e75ff090726516649353e03a","tid":356902,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"成隻大脾都係啲釘嘅傷口仲沖涼 諗到都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92051a64952fe35d22cfa396ae1abbf23fd3def8","tid":356902,"uid":102096,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e14207026866efe17a2dc97898bc73e9884a380","tid":356902,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:26:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55bd6924bd1299c543d9a1d42df3a7463aa33182","tid":356902,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"呢單嘢就算係真，咁處理法真係幾唔人道。"},{"pid":"d0f470a65dd936895885576ad8fdcc5cd11abd2a","tid":356902,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>據李柱銘所講，林生係西貢醒返之後<br />\n係返咗屋企先，仲要沖涼同洗咗當時身穿嘅衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度講有沖涼呀？"},{"pid":"a9324db9684918cc30504f01ebbeaf193c0d1afe","tid":356902,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>據李柱銘所講，林生係西貢醒返之後<br />\n係返咗屋企先，仲要沖涼同洗咗當時身穿嘅衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n預左開記招留證據俾記者影相"},{"pid":"4abf22606ba1e20a3712729e924df658bed990ca","tid":356902,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"手洗定機洗🤣"},{"pid":"9cf92fd903ed12514493e5150ed6ab53632e7649","tid":356902,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>據李柱銘所講，林生係西貢醒返之後<br />\n係返咗屋企先，仲要沖涼同洗咗當時身穿嘅衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度講有沖涼呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港電台新聞<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1347821-20170812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1347821-20170812.htm&d=98m4kCksxFEIJSHFkFyK%2BkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a17a0c2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1347821-20170812.htm&h=66342669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1347821-20170812.htm</a><br />\n[/url]「報稱被內地人員帶走禁錮和毆打的民主黨成員林子健早上出院，他表示先向傳媒交代事件，再報警的做法，是經民主黨創黨主席李柱銘及前主席何俊仁商討後決定。<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘出席活動後表示，林子健在凌晨3時半用手機傳送了一些受傷的照片給他，他在早上6時半起床看到時嚇了一跳。李柱銘之後與何俊仁討論，認為不能不公布，他們決定先召開記者會。<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘表示，並不知道幕後指使人士，現時不能說是由強力部門所做，又指林子健沒有法律常識要保留證據，形容<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對方回家後洗澡及清洗衣服</span></strong>的做法愚蠢。」"},{"pid":"4a79f325f46f221c4770e9a263db160560888aa6","tid":356902,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢單嘢就算係真，咁處理法真係幾唔人道。</blockquote><br />\n兩個民主黨大佬做法唔人道又冇必要<br />\n被打者又唔夠精，應該留證據增加自己口供既可信性<br />\n<br />\n如果最後冇任何片或人證明到林生被捉上車<br />\n成晚所發生既事，除左林生自己既口供同身上十幾口釘之外<br />\n就冇其他證據"},{"pid":"0416b2f20102af78c529df70908253e00f5fa81b","tid":356902,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T18:53:02.000Z","msg":"講過無數次架啦<br />\n炒過咁多次都仲係咁<br />\n呢鑊衰埋既真係冇眼睇"},{"pid":"a2a4be4bf3e7ee21fd28514eaf0628c9368a81ab","tid":356902,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T18:58:41.000Z","msg":"佢仲有國安既WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n林子健又指，暫不便公開3日前曾來電警告他的內地人士，但指對方是在他過去出任民主黨中委時，已有接觸，事發後他再沒有致電對方，指對方過去自稱身份是來自北京的國安，曾自稱「係中央直接嗰條線」，3日前是用WhatsApp電話與他溝通。"},{"pid":"034ff2a2bb9d3b8d65b6e72d6350dd97af3af216","tid":356902,"uid":6192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T19:07:23.000Z","msg":"唔係唔想信白鴿<br />\n但要搞都唔係搞過無咩人識既搞<br />\n佢做過咩要比人咁高調搞先<br />\n就係因為打左幾句所以咁？<br />\n話佢得罪人可信d囉"},{"pid":"5742e4819a8594858b5fb341ab6ccf1d798f67c4","tid":356902,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T19:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢單嘢就算係真，咁處理法真係幾唔人道。</blockquote><br />\n兩個民主黨大佬做法唔人道又冇必要<br />\n被打者又唔夠精，應該留證據增加自己口供既可信性<br />\n<br />\n如果最後冇任何片或人證明到林生被捉上車<br />\n成晚所發生既事，除左林生自己既口供同身上十幾口釘之外<br />\n就冇其他證據</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知道唔拆得釘但又走去洗衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哩點好周星馳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0fc7624f7adca53a1c3a1540187bcdd69de0a6","tid":356902,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T19:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢單嘢就算係真，咁處理法真係幾唔人道。</blockquote><br />\n兩個民主黨大佬做法唔人道又冇必要<br />\n被打者又唔夠精，應該留證據增加自己口供既可信性<br />\n<br />\n如果最後冇任何片或人證明到林生被捉上車<br />\n成晚所發生既事，除左林生自己既口供同身上十幾口釘之外<br />\n就冇其他證據</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知道唔拆得釘但又走去洗衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哩點好周星馳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n件衫絕對係證據 佢就走左去洗左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能驗到捉佢班人既頭髮 而家乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n一係就有cam影到佢比人捉上車 影埋車牌"},{"pid":"f156db01711765fb86c7a2c14a691a2e2fb34aa6","tid":356902,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢單野真係唔好跟車太貼,好易炒車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李波單野又係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe03ef1fd4596ef6227a6a7aae5271d630a01971","tid":356902,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:27:20.000Z","msg":"😂😂"},{"pid":"ba53fec5938bbb9cbf10b027747b3aa594f0181c","tid":356902,"uid":71133,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:37:12.000Z","msg":"五毛空湧而出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證明單野係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9921e27fa9d1a51081b32ef4c46384c5883b5e38","tid":356902,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:40:27.000Z","msg":"唔理鬼唔鬼<br />\n喂 呀哥 嗰啲證據黎架"},{"pid":"417796e5dd2b1ad3aee84dd1a28b49842f03e2a9","tid":356902,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:57:52.000Z","